headline: Dynatrace and ServiceNow Deepen Strategic Collaboration to Advance Autonomous IT Operations
summary: BOSTON & SANTA CLARA, Calif., October 27, 2025--Dynatrace (NYSE: DT), the leading AI-powered observability platform, and ServiceNow (NYSE: NOW), the AI platform for business transformation, today announced a multi-year strategic collaboration to advance autonomous IT operations and scale intelligent automation for joint enterprise customers.
